    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab><persName ref="#people/3306">Ademari</persName>
                        <rs key="#childOf">filio</rs>
                        <persName ref="#people/3307" key="#parentOf">bone memorie
                            Eriprandi</persName>, riceve da <persName ref="#people/3305"
                            key="#Bishops">Hieremias</persName> gratia Dei huius Sancte Lucane
                        ecclesie humilis <rs key="#Bishops">episcopus</rs>, per cartula livellario
                        ordine ad censum vobis perexolvendum (…) id est <rs key="#Mills">molino</rs>
                        illo in <rs key="#Rivers">fluvio Salabro</rs>, prope <placeName
                            ref="#places/753" key="#Rivers #Mills">Teupascio</placeName>, quas ego
                        ipse edificavi in terra istius <rs key="#Mother_churches">episcopatui</rs>
                        vestro <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/68" key="#Mother_churches">Sancti
                            Martini</orgName>, <rs key="#Fines">finibus</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Fines">Maritimense</placeName>; iam dicto molino cum omni
                        conciatura suas, sive terra, qualiter ego eas modo ad manus mea abere visu
                        sum (…). Censo: ad parte ipsius episcopatui (…) per singulos annos per omne
                        mense ianuario, (…) ad <geogName ref="#estates/3305"
                            key="#Curtes #Mother_churches"><rs key="#Curtes">curte vestra illa
                                domnicata</rs> in loco <placeName ref="#places/544" key="#Curtes"
                                >Casale Longo</placeName></geogName>, per nos aut per misso nostro,
                        vobis vel ad locoposito vestro argentum denarios bono expendiviles numero
                        sex tantum (…). Pena: argentum soledos quinquaginta (…). <persName
                            key="#Writer #Notary"><name ref="Adalfredus">Adalfridi</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> scrive due <rs
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis">cartulas</rs>. Actum <placeName
                            ref="#places/4" key="#Mother_churches #Bishops">Luca</placeName>.</ab>
                    <ab>Sottoscrivono come <rs key="#Witness">testimoni</rs>: <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Teobaldus">Teopaldo</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Iohannes">Ioannes</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Adalfredus"
                            >Adalfridi</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Albertus">Alpertus</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"
                                ><name ref="Teobaldus">Teutpaldus</name></persName>
                        <persName>qd. <name ref="Adalfredus">Adalfridi</name></persName>. </ab>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div type="bibliography" subtype="editions">
                <p>ChLA, 82, n. 35, pp. 120-121; MDL, 5/2, n. 904, p. 488</p>
            </div>
